{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"API Collection","role":"collectionGroup","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"title":"Provisioning Virtual Machines"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Choosing a Mode","level":3,"anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode","type":"heading"},{"header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Mode"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Status"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Works without setup?","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Network needed?","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Best for","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Working"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Need SSH enabled","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Cloned VMs with SSH","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"In progress","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Planned","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need agent installed"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OCI images (future)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Planned","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need watcher"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"No-disk-modify environments","type":"text"}]}]]],"type":"table"},{"text":"SSH (Working)","level":3,"anchor":"SSH-Working","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"],"syntax":"bash","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Requires:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)","level":3,"anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"],"syntax":"bash","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Guest Agent (Planned)","level":3,"anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is planned for a future release."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Shared Folder (Planned)","level":3,"anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"mode is planned for a future release."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Provisioning"},"sections":[],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"],["